    {
      "name": "Blood Transfers",
      "description": "TransferController \u2014 /api/transfers\n\nFull transfer saga: PENDING \u2192 APPROVED \u2192 COMPLETED\n\nState machine:\n  PENDING \u2192 APPROVED | REJECTED | CANCELLED | INSUFFICIENT_STOCK\n  APPROVED \u2192 COMPLETED | CANCELLED | EXPIRED (48h auto-expire)\n\nWorkflow:\n1. Clinician searches blood (Blood Search folder)\n2. POST /api/transfers \u2014 creates request, reserves stock immediately\n3. Officer at source hospital: GET /api/transfers/pending \u2192 PUT /{id}/approve or /{id}/reject\n4. Officer at destination hospital: PUT /{id}/complete with unitsReceived\n5. Either party: PUT /{id}/cancel (APPROVED cancel releases reservation)\n\nAll requests require Authorization: Bearer {{token}}.\nSet {{transferId}} from the Create response.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Transfer Request",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.success && json.data && json.data.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('transferId', json.data.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sourceHospitalId\": 1,\n  \"bloodGroup\": \"O+\",\n  \"quantity\": 3,\n  \"idempotencyKey\": \"req-001-2026-06-16\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers"
              ]
            },
            "description": "TRANS-1: Submit a blood transfer request.\n\nRoles: CLINICIAN, OFFICER, ADMIN\n\nErrors:\n- 400: quantity \u2264 0, invalid blood group\n- 400: sourceHospitalId == own hospital\n- 409: duplicate idempotencyKey (double-click protection)\n- 409: source hospital deactivated\n- 409: insufficient stock at source (live check, not search index)\n\nAuto-saves transferId \u2192 {{transferId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Requests",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/my-requests",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "my-requests"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns all transfer requests submitted by the authenticated user's hospital."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Pending Requests (Officer view)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/pending",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "pending"
              ]
            },
            "description": "OFFICER/ADMIN only. Returns PENDING requests targeting the authenticated user's hospital."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve Transfer",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/{{transferId}}/approve",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "{{transferId}}",
                "approve"
              ]
            },
            "description": "TRANS-2: Approve a PENDING request.\n\nRoles: OFFICER, ADMIN (must belong to source hospital)\n\nErrors:\n- 403: officer belongs to a different hospital\n- 409: request was cancelled before approval\n- 409: concurrent approval \u2014 exactly one succeeds (optimistic locking)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject Transfer",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"No compatible stock available at this time\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/{{transferId}}/reject",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "{{transferId}}",
                "reject"
              ]
            },
            "description": "TRANS-3: Reject a PENDING request with a mandatory reason.\n\nRoles: OFFICER, ADMIN (must belong to source hospital)\n\nErrors:\n- 400: reason is missing\n- 409: request is already APPROVED (state machine enforced)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete Transfer (full receipt)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"unitsReceived\": 3\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/{{transferId}}/complete",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "{{transferId}}",
                "complete"
              ]
            },
            "description": "TRANS-4: Confirm full receipt. Source deducts approved quantity; destination gains received units.\n\nRoles: OFFICER, CLINICIAN, ADMIN (must belong to requesting hospital)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete Transfer (partial receipt / breakage)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"unitsReceived\": 2\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/{{transferId}}/complete",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "{{transferId}}",
                "complete"
              ]
            },
            "description": "TRANS-4 partial: fewer units arrived than approved (breakage/loss).\nSource deducts full approved amount; destination adds only received units. Discrepancy is audit-logged."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete Transfer (all expired in transit)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"unitsReceived\": 0\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/{{transferId}}/complete",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "{{transferId}}",
                "complete"
              ]
            },
            "description": "TRANS-4 expired-in-transit: unitsReceived=0 means all blood expired during transit.\nReservation is released; nothing is added to destination."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel Transfer (PENDING)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/{{transferId}}/cancel",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "transfers",
                "{{transferId}}",
                "cancel"
              ]
            },
            "description": "TRANS-5: Cancel a PENDING or APPROVED request.\n\nPENDING \u2192 reservation released.\nAPPROVED \u2192 reservation released (compensating action).\nCOMPLETED \u2192 409 (cannot cancel).\n\nRoles: CLINICIAN/OFFICER at requesting hospital, or officer at source hospital."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
